{"tid":324830,"cid":25,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］兩個月貓bb一唔見人就叫得好大聲","createTime":"2017-07-16T17:34:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-17T15:25:37.000Z","uid":8234,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b978b8b6a2e01cd20d73da8ae9060f5c2261329","tid":324830,"uid":8234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e7f9c456d8ce4c556c0d38cd0230b0c6d8b89905","tid":324830,"uid":28624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T17:40:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a82c89b9988520d782adf5219634da603874277a","tid":324830,"uid":8234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T18:11:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affb1fa1c85bb5e5cc3f8e18d30d7a48e114af7c","tid":324830,"uid":89793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T18:14:13.000Z","msg":"好多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05c883cee3ccaa7d734ad44deaee2c2170901a54","tid":324830,"uid":8234,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T18:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好鐘意喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時同佢對望都會細細聲喵<br />\n仲好嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日都要痴住人、撩人地玩<br />\n唔知係咪因為性格太嗲所以咁唔獨立，成日要人陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a3312629a04086aabc7b07060dff4a834837c50b","tid":324830,"uid":50893,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T18:39:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>好多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好鐘意喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時同佢對望都會細細聲喵<br />\n仲好嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日都要痴住人、撩人地玩<br />\n唔知係咪因為性格太嗲所以咁唔獨立，成日要人陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我隻貓都係好嗲，會成日叫我去摸佢，同佢玩，你可以試下得閒先陪佢玩，平時就由佢叫，佢叫得多知道冇人理佢就會收聲，又或者隻貓仲細，冇左媽媽冇安全感，可以試下整個地方佢訓，比隻公仔陪佢，tum 下佢訓"},{"pid":"58b7b95ab9861988b4425f4fecadd8245e6ad032","tid":324830,"uid":8234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T18:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>好多野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好鐘意喵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時同佢對望都會細細聲喵<br />\n仲好嗲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 成日都要痴住人、撩人地玩<br />\n唔知係咪因為性格太嗲所以咁唔獨立，成日要人陪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我隻貓都係好嗲，會成日叫我去摸佢，同佢玩，你可以試下得閒先陪佢玩，平時就由佢叫，佢叫得多知道冇人理佢就會收聲，又或者隻貓仲細，冇左媽媽冇安全感，可以試下整個地方佢訓，比隻公仔陪佢，tum 下佢訓</blockquote><br />\n我試過唔理佢，佢會衝埋黎咬我手指、腳指同頭髮，又或者跳上我個身，引我注意要我同佢玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平時佢見到我係佢視線範圍就唔會叫，不過唔會俾機會我唔理佢<br />\n我買咗張貓床俾佢，佢唔瞓淨係要痴住我瞓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一定要瞓係我頭頂/頭側邊嗰啲位，如果我坐係度佢就要瞓我大脾或者肚，唔肯瞓床<br />\n我都覺得佢係因為太早離開貓媽媽先咁，咁等佢大個啲係咪會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46a1c9f222b38d6c20bc4327a23dc6132ac7ad4a","tid":324830,"uid":8234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T19:03:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想佢可以獨立啲，佢叫得咁慘心都痛埋"},{"pid":"818f78790e8d83a792f45da0dc177adc034b8505","tid":324830,"uid":124322,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:31:23.000Z","msg":"好好珍惜呢啲時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大個左叫都唔睬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39fbb85fff08083e3f1d55948e83d6b803314eca","tid":324830,"uid":5791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:41:45.000Z","msg":"如果再大d 都係咁，夠六個月就帶佢絕育"},{"pid":"dcf7f78033acb918598480e6a32c0e806ef1d83d","tid":324830,"uid":76399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:44:28.000Z","msg":"好似少咁啲嘢喎個Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"998511106967c320667243fb88b9cbe54b87e425","tid":324830,"uid":16892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-16T23:49:42.000Z","msg":"圖都冇張點討論"},{"pid":"095babe5608632839c7375c690b9aa95302b8281","tid":324830,"uid":8234,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:58:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好好珍惜呢啲時光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大個左叫都唔睬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都明白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實佢嗲我叫我嗰陣我好開心，不過當我出去返學佢叫到我係𨋢口都聽到好大聲，搞到我心掛掛又擔心騷擾到鄰居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc60f1cce1c2cd9b7b7c4ee8c27b162a2cc1828","tid":324830,"uid":8234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T03:58:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果再大d 都係咁，夠六個月就帶佢絕育</blockquote><br />\n係咪因為發情期都會叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a854945e4b278b8fb03a0ea143601fb08e80c6ab","tid":324830,"uid":123304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T04:00:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好似少咁啲嘢喎個Post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n圖"},{"pid":"abc76c392a096c6c005e8cace7cfe2e22b491123","tid":324830,"uid":33220,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-17T04:00:21.000Z","msg":"2個月先係咁咋 大多幾個月彩你有味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3